elements.2211.03280_c04a5ca00709be9233faf4bbcc18e: This paper focuses on the task of survival time analysis for lung cancer
elements.2211.03280_ac8eea9a71632e81b36e583be1d7b: Although much progress has been made in this problem in recent years, the performance of existing methods is still far from satisfactory
elements.2211.03280_3cd06970bb1182d5e28a9a046daee: Traditional and some deep learning- based survival time analyses for lung cancer are mostly based on textual clinical information such as staging, age, histology, etc
elements.2211.03280_d9b6505e731d81121565547f50a44: Unlike existing methods that predicting on the single modality, we observe that a human clinician usually takes multimodal data such as text clinical data and visual scans to estimate survival time
elements.2211.03280_dc568701bb1e631585d2aa048ddfb: Motivated by this, in this work, we contribute a smart cross-modality network for survival analysis network named Lite-ProSENet that simulates a human's manner of decision making
elements.2211.03280_d3e788516824d19a6e550d9ca3df3: To be specific, Lite-ProSENet is a two-tower architecture that takes the clinical data and the CT scans as inputs to create the survival prediction
elements.2211.03280_902a3ad8666d090ba3b2dc983c17a: The textural tower is responsible for modelling the clinical data, we build a light transformer using multi-head self-attention as our textural tower
elements.2211.03280_2322e60c25f72b0265686e02d0bfc: The visual tower (namely ProSENet) is responsible for extracting features from the CT scans
elements.2211.03280_9e08eeb2a3df224f7a08d21552712: The backbone of ProSENet is a 3D Resnet that works together with several repeatable building block named 3D-SE Resblock for a compact feature extraction
elements.2211.03280_69eeba1ac7017a2e4240c95d834c2: Our 3D-SE Resblock is composed of a 3D channel âSqueeze-and-Excitationâ (SE) block and a temporal SE block
elements.2211.03280_9d04a257f9969c1042905f6ac78e4: The purpose of 3D-SE Resblock is to adaptively select the valuable features from CT scans
elements.2211.03280_aa951f3bc79663ce605f493bca729: Besides, to further filter out the redundant information among CT scans, we develop a simple but effective frame difference mechanism that takes the performance of our model to the new state- of-the-art
elements.2211.03280_4c58b03ea0ac9feeac22c1694701d: Extensive experiments were conducted using data from 422 NSCLC patients from The Cancer Imaging Archive (TCIA)
elements.2211.03280_407345b8326e27a2bd4e787018f6b: The results show that our Lite-ProSENet outperforms favorably again all comparison methods and achieves the new state of the art with the 89.3
elements.2211.03280_ac508432b2564099a4d4f453e90be: The code will be made publicly available.
elements.2211.03280_fa3ae71ba40b9a88cafd661bd5b92: Lung cancer is one of the most dangerous diseases, the overall five-year survival rate for lung cancer (LC) is even less than 20
elements.2211.03280_86b72ff8889fbc2abeab55f7bc29d: Most lung cancers can be divided into two broad histological subtypes: non-small cell lung cancer (NS-
elements.2211.03280_d47d41324d717cddd5ba6af3148c1: CLC) and small cell lung cancer (SCLC)
elements.2211.03280_c49d660a0504e3dbea094f7e9d897: Compared to SCLC, NSCLC accounts for the majority of diagnoses and is less aggressive
elements.2211.03280_60b1387b5763cda5d89450d760881: NSCLC spreads and grows more slowly than SCLC and causes few or no symptoms until it is advanced
elements.2211.03280_e3717bd27028d39bcff9119f4f905: As a result, patients are usually not detected until it is at a later stage
elements.2211.03280_f43bfd974b3a77fc821bb90774038: And it has caused millions of deaths in both women and men
elements.2211.03280_3e3c8f5a408fadb524d77d3343852: Lung cancer survival analysis, or prognostication, of lung cancer attempts to model the time range for a given event of interest (biological death), from the beginning of follow-up until the occurrence of the event
elements.2211.03280_2bc2e6c0542a13fc40990ec172da7: The survival model is an estimate of how lung cancer will develop, and it can reveal the relationship between prognostic factors and the disease
elements.2211.03280_aff00641eb0e1098963c9ce1dd122: Using the accurate prognostic models, doctors can determine the most likely development(s) of the patient's cancer
elements.2211.03280_3d9ac698fdb3f0b68fd02e827b4d8: To improve predictive accuracy and automate the NSCLC survival analysis process, as well as to assist medical experts develop precise treatment solutions, we aim to explore a novel method for NSCLC survival analysis.
elements.2211.03280_8bd309dcd2ecf3cd7682e82bc8ff6: Traditional statistical methods for survival analysis leverage structured data from comprehensive medical examinations of a patient
elements.2211.03280_fe1e62cf3f36b313af10ba6c0c6ec: Traditional methods mainly include time-to-event modelling tools such as the Cox proportional hazards (Cox- PH) model
elements.2211.03280_fbf02f0bc4b144921e34b482d54df: Besides, survival analysis based on machine learning is also a popular branch, such as survival trees
elements.2211.03280_cad7e41e907bbdb8683dc18fbd76f: These models assume that the hazard ratio between two subjects is constant over time
elements.2211.03280_5022cdef1471e1ebdb8ce836a7482: and estimate either a risk score or the time-to-event distribution
elements.2211.03280_bed174e05fefeb3b31b45b1afc7a1: However, when implemented in clinical practise, the interaction between covariates is complex and all these methods focus only on structured data, overlooking the enormous information within the unstructured data such as CT scans
elements.2211.03280_1dd3f7e80130cb57a8e09d1360f1e: Moreover, medical experts usually have to dedicate extesive efforts in introducing the hand-crafted features
elements.2211.03280_d4c107a4a3947f0b4a21ebcc1d48e: Recently, some works have been proposed using pathological images and demonstrating the effectiveness of features from images
elements.2211.03280_6e44c263fa4b9439ada0c1029a890: However, pathological images require a lung biopsy
elements.2211.03280_6e8755cb9a712ccaaceea3d74ceee: Moreover, the process of obtaining pathological images is invasive and associated with potential health risks such as pneumothorax, bleeding, infection, systemic air embolism and other side effects, which is a consequence of abnormal results of non-invasive computed tomography (CT) for lung cancer screening
elements.2211.03280_1392fa74295cd6894517a55d7df6f: Artificial intelligence has witnessed rapid progress in the last decade
elements.2211.03280_f455f816f3588f56e69995f3afebc: With the development of deep learning techniques, it has accomplished remarkable success in various fields of research such as natural language processing, computer vision, etc
elements.2211.03280_9ba2a1589a5c51d8a5520985e483f: As a cutting-edge technology, deep learning has the potential to offer great potential for medical diagnostics
elements.2211.03280_1d75a27d6aeb464c526fd8ad01c70: Some of the most innovative and novel deep learning methods have been successfully applied to the diagnosis of lung cancer using CT images and the performance even outperformed human experts
elements.2211.03280_97d9456e77a6ac32201c3e53a59c9: However, existing deep learning-based methods only consider the structured or visual cues
elements.2211.03280_6c8b022f1a8b75cefe789cf52c00d: In contrast, medical experts often consider clinical data and visual information such as CT images together to make a comprehensive decision
elements.2211.03280_fd2498d9db73297777fe4ecb6aff6: Consequently, the prediction of current methods is not reliable and credible enough
elements.2211.03280_e6ff30f7b888d040ace619dcf3f32: To address this weakness, we proposed a novel multimodal paradigm for lung cancer survival analysis inspired by the success of deep learning
elements.2211.03280_f2bbe3f1566cd5d31b4737fe69cb8: To successfully build such a multimodal network, the first challenge is to encode the task-friendly features from different modalities
elements.2211.03280_342fb0902f66c2cc3f55ee5ffb96b: The form of the clinical data looks like some discrete symbols in the diagram, but they are essentially highly correlated with each other in essence
elements.2211.03280_910580360d28544c7765cceaa7da9: Therefore, to find correlations between different words, a Light transformer network is proposed for processing the textual clinical data
elements.2211.03280_cb0d721e915a1b61ae9f9474d8ef9: The core building block of our model is the multi-head self-attention
elements.2211.03280_1e24d243db2acdeabce1ef7128a2d: Moreover, self-attention mechanism is capable of correlate different disease factors to capture more information
elements.2211.03280_fde1704822d1ab2385b593c531360: CT slices contain rich spatial and temporal information
elements.2211.03280_346d514d6044e664ddba57b328817: , we adopt 3D Resnet as a backbone for feature extraction
elements.2211.03280_92eab3b5f44e7a3af4367d7d4b933: However, we found that there is too much redundant information in both the spatial and temporal dimensions, which severely prevents the model from perceiving the most important components in the visual information
elements.2211.03280_037a792e7b4a82e7c2a756f5c46b4: To alleviate this problem, we for the first time propose a 3D channel SE block and a 3D temporal SE block
elements.2211.03280_9cca7c12b6e4d57fd8e79a0f1370d: Both blocks are integrated into the original residual module to form an architecture specifically for NSCLC prognosis, namely ProgSE-Net
elements.2211.03280_8e09ba1bc980acb69825048ec5fbe: Moreover, we also observe that the pixels in adjacent CT slices are similar or the same in most cases
elements.2211.03280_99445477c443a4ffd02a47a14c8db: To support the ProgSE-Net, we further propose a mechanism of frame difference
elements.2211.03280_e9f9860cd86e20f28e6d426350bde: The proposed frame difference creates two additional CT slices by subtracting the adjacent pixels in two directions, which is an effective strategy in our practise
elements.2211.03280_a907bdd34e07b31c47dd44ef43fca: Finally, considering the above, we develop the first multimodal network for NSCLC survival analysis, which takes Deep Learning-based NSCLC survival analysis one step forward by simultaneously considering the textual clinical data and the visual CT clues
elements.2211.03280_51052ddb0f4f90a4048c220dea48f: , our network is a two-tower paradigm,
elements.2211.03280_450bcf9c5c434aafd28f24fe1bc5b: , clinical tower and a visual tower
elements.2211.03280_2d3de1b39e98dd0dc7db5633f8314: The clinical tower is responsible for encoding the clinical data, while the visual tower aims to extract the visual representation from the CT images
elements.2211.03280_48d10152474c9e7e5124ce39f2736: Finally, the prediction head fuses the cross-modality features and provides the time prediction
elements.2211.03280_63dbc737d586c9e69693c789a7199: In summary, the key contributions associated with the Lite-ProSENet can be highlighted as follows:
elements.2211.03280_451e66f86346eed718393058b4208: The first application of a two-tower DNN to survival analysis of NSCLC using structured data and CT images simultaneously.
elements.2211.03280_9a2cef46c075e2e39dcdbd722fad0: The first application of transformer and 3DSE-Net block to multimodal clinical data for disease prognosis.
elements.2211.03280_112e11d2f49207739cf3916e6812d: Results on benchmark and real-world clinical datasets demonstrate that Lite-ProSENet outperforms SOTA methods by a substantial margin.

elements.2211.03280_65c588a3910aae785cd27f45b38f3: In section IV, we present the experiments and ablation studies
elements.2211.03280_344c6d4294681e587e5a665712675: We discuss some choices when building our network and the included hyper-parameters in section V. Finally, the conclusion and future work are given in section VI

elements.2211.03280_a6a90de4f26bd381cf91c852b0a7c: In this paper, we proposed a fully automated end-to-end multimodal deep network framework for NSCLC survival analysis
elements.2211.03280_fda96798196f4c8654d7ebfbefb38: Our framework can learn complementary representations from the CT image and non-image clinical data modalities
elements.2211.03280_ab939ea51fea200fcb9e8e71e06d4: Extensive experimental results show that DeepMMSA outperforms conventional methods that use a single source of information alone
elements.2211.03280_fffb9a15cd2461a9e36b508afe4f1: But there is still some future work to do
elements.2211.03280_b1a550a0556ba4827d55b81e27125: There are some potential ways to improve the performance of the proposed framework.
elements.2211.03280_feb12e0bf000fea20e8d0df82b6dc: Since there are three basic modules for multimodal deep learning survival analysis framework, we consider to made improvements based on the following three aspects:
elements.2211.03280_2b2ae4b6da554919f8a69b54cce3a: Provide more complementary information by adding more modalities to improve the performance, such as e-nose based diagnosis
elements.2211.03280_bc9e20034c617a569b00cdad65006: time series data, etc., and try to fully exploit the inherent correlations across multiple modalities.
elements.2211.03280_e3ca17101a9ff0d80072534a404c6: Perform different multimodal fusion approaches, such as decision fusion and hybrid fusion method, etc.
elements.2211.03280_355e3e275ace53fdb882f78749071: In the survival analysis module, theoretically, we can use any survival analysis model, such as cox-time, deepsurv, to improve the performance of our proposed framework.
elements.2211.03280_4ba69fe2eb496583fe9fbe9ff2419: This work contributes a powerful multimodal network for more accurate prediction of NSCLC survival, with the purpose of helping clinicians to develop timely treatment plans and improve patients' quality of life
elements.2211.03280_57fca673c069451b2bbf9b9d347d6: Our method provides a new state-of-the-art result of 89.3
elements.2211.03280_c04b67ce77f2afc81658f2f5c79cb: To well model the cross-modal data, we develop a two-tower network, with the textual tower responsible for the clinical data and the visual tower for the CT slices
elements.2211.03280_dafc917499ae21bf946ea67c302a3: Inspired by the success of the transformer in the NLP field, we propose a very light transformer using the core of self-attention
elements.2211.03280_d9e572ac254df4be5d58b85f8a01b: For the visual tower, we design a ProSENet based on the 3D- SE Resblock, where channel Squeeze-and-excitation and temporal Squeeze-and-excitation are proposed to suppress the redundant information among the CT slices
elements.2211.03280_4a25c3df5cd093352b90d6510e8fe: Besides, we further introduce a frame difference mechanism to help promote our network up to the new state-of-the-art in terms of C-index and MAE
elements.2211.03280_29931d9431f68e67cde65b7750d72: In experiments, we conduct comparisons, ablation studies and discussions that well verify the superiority of our Lite-ProSENet
elements.2211.03280_27ba03420797ea923d174a66e454b: The practice of this work gives us much confidence about the deep learning-based survival analysis
elements.2211.03280_418fc0bbaecd8cb9b6ca3bc594bb3: We believe that the deep learning-based method has great potential to be realized for survival time analysis
elements.2211.03280_cbf7762af0ce9f270c4a716263bcf: In the future, we will further investigate this problem from the following two aspects:
elements.2211.03280_27595917410c1994cd77a71665923: In this work, the fusion of multimodal features is simple, we simply concatenate the features from Lite-transformer and ProSENet
elements.2211.03280_cce1665b2f3694aea1486789ab0c4: In the future we will explore more effective fusion manners.
